# Re-include the dialog-smoke fixture artifact so a fresh Claude session
# has a tangible .ams.json to compare against without rerunning the
# `cargo run --bin produce_dialog_smoke` binary first.  The binary
# regenerates this file deterministically; tracking it keeps the schema
# reviewable in PR diffs.
!test-output/
!test-output/tauri-project-dialogs-smoke/
!test-output/tauri-project-dialogs-smoke/native-dialog-save-as.ams.json

